WEBVTT

01:37.060 --> 01:40.940
[The Best Thing]

01:41.530 --> 01:48.560
[Episode 23: Fox Nuts]
[Sweet and astringent in taste and neutral in nature. They're associated with the spleen and kidney meridians. They strengthen the kidneys, secure essence, eliminate dampness, and relieve vaginal discharge.]

02:07.530 --> 02:08.850
What are you doing here?

02:09.680 --> 02:10.440
I just came to check out

02:10.470 --> 02:12.210
my girlfriend's work environment.

02:14.380 --> 02:15.220
Looks pretty good.

02:15.350 --> 02:18.820
♫When I see you♫

02:20.670 --> 02:24.020
♫Flowers bloom♫

02:25.020 --> 02:28.590
♫When I see you♫

02:28.230 --> 02:29.600
Are you really working overtime?

02:30.340 --> 02:34.020
♫Flowers bloom♫

02:30.790 --> 02:31.700
Of course.

02:35.310 --> 02:36.190
Alright then.

02:36.250 --> 02:37.850
I was thinking about

02:37.910 --> 02:39.270
picking my girlfriend up from work.

02:44.420 --> 02:45.700
Get some good rest tonight.

02:46.060 --> 02:46.940
See you tomorrow.

02:53.620 --> 02:54.850
I don't want to wait until tomorrow.

02:56.170 --> 02:58.120
Can't we meet tonight?

02:57.550 --> 03:05.350
♫Nothing in this world can take me away from you♫

03:00.510 --> 03:01.200
Okay.

03:07.390 --> 03:14.010
♫Nothing in this world can take me away from you♫

03:11.670 --> 03:12.480
He Suye.

03:13.740 --> 03:15.500
Keep a safe distance of 10 meters.

03:16.990 --> 03:20.660
♫When I'm with you♫

03:18.500 --> 03:20.270
What safe distance?

03:21.790 --> 03:25.760
♫When I'm with you♫

03:36.000 --> 03:37.120
Professor He.

03:37.610 --> 03:38.450
Hello.

03:39.190 --> 03:40.240
Is there anything I can help you with?

03:40.240 --> 03:41.750
No. I'm just going to have breakfast.

03:42.160 --> 03:43.510
Alright. This way, please.

03:47.470 --> 03:48.700
I want to ask you something.

03:49.260 --> 03:51.370
Are you and He Suye

03:51.400 --> 03:52.240
very close?

03:54.390 --> 03:55.480
He's my boyfriend.

04:00.640 --> 04:01.400
I see.

04:01.740 --> 04:02.390
Good.

04:05.160 --> 04:06.000
So, you...

04:06.020 --> 04:07.690
you haven't been together for long, have you?

04:08.130 --> 04:09.600
He was with me during the Spring Festival.

04:09.630 --> 04:11.720
I never heard him mention you.

04:12.060 --> 04:14.910
Yeah, we started dating after the Spring Festival.

04:15.990 --> 04:16.990
I see.

04:19.370 --> 04:21.130
Well, I'm quite curious.

04:21.160 --> 04:24.230
You two are in completely different professions.

04:24.550 --> 04:25.870
Do you have much to talk about?

04:26.310 --> 04:27.630
Are you saying that

04:27.630 --> 04:28.720
people in different professions

04:28.720 --> 04:29.870
can't be together?

04:29.870 --> 04:30.820
That's not what I mean.

04:31.600 --> 04:33.640
We actually have a lot in common.

04:34.140 --> 04:35.870
For example, this sachet in your hand—

04:36.070 --> 04:37.150
he made it.

04:37.480 --> 04:38.960
It's an anise sachet

04:39.040 --> 04:40.240
that dispels cold and regulates qi.

04:40.430 --> 04:42.040
And the medicated diet in this restaurant,

04:42.070 --> 04:43.430
he and his team designed it.

04:43.670 --> 04:44.400
How do you like it?

04:44.420 --> 04:45.180
It's good, right?

04:45.210 --> 04:46.090
It's excellent.

04:48.190 --> 04:49.720
It's fate

04:49.720 --> 04:50.630
that brought you together.

04:51.580 --> 04:52.850
He Suye

04:52.880 --> 04:54.170
works in oncology.

04:54.510 --> 04:55.360
I'm a physician too,

04:55.360 --> 04:56.560
so I know he has to

04:56.870 --> 04:58.830
deal with life-and-death situations every day.

04:58.990 --> 05:00.750
I'm worried that it might weigh on him.

05:01.280 --> 05:02.190
So, if you can,

05:02.270 --> 05:04.360
please take good care of him.

05:04.950 --> 05:06.180
Don't worry.

05:06.200 --> 05:07.800
Your concern is unnecessary.

05:07.870 --> 05:10.320
Actually, He Suye is a really positive person.

05:10.340 --> 05:11.680
He knows exactly what he wants.

05:12.190 --> 05:12.750
Really?

05:13.280 --> 05:14.010
I don't believe it.

05:15.690 --> 05:16.610
I don't

05:17.170 --> 05:18.560
talk to him much,

05:19.020 --> 05:21.410
so I don't really know how he's doing these days.

05:25.550 --> 05:27.790
He's giving a research presentation tomorrow afternoon.

05:28.160 --> 05:29.600
If you can attend it,

05:29.730 --> 05:31.050
he'd be really happy.

05:33.450 --> 05:34.050
Alright.

05:34.070 --> 05:35.030
I'll go eat first.

05:35.060 --> 05:36.420
Okay. Enjoy your breakfast.

06:05.940 --> 06:06.670
By the way,

06:07.070 --> 06:09.300
I found out Mr. He's room number

06:09.390 --> 06:10.800
and told the housekeeping staff

06:10.800 --> 06:11.720
to take extra care of him.

06:13.240 --> 06:14.050
Thanks.

06:18.930 --> 06:19.900
But…

06:21.750 --> 06:23.640
why don't you visit him yourself?

06:30.410 --> 06:31.170
That's not necessary.

06:31.850 --> 06:33.260
I don't have much

06:33.290 --> 06:34.650
to say to him.

06:36.190 --> 06:37.800
As long as he's comfortable staying there, it's enough.

06:49.990 --> 06:52.190
The tension between you and him…

06:54.090 --> 06:56.790
isn't just because you chose TCM, is it?

07:06.780 --> 07:08.390
Does it

07:09.130 --> 07:11.010
have something to do with Mrs. Shen too?

07:19.930 --> 07:21.410
When my mom was fighting cancer,

07:22.660 --> 07:25.020
he was too engrossed in his studies to be around.

07:26.890 --> 07:28.180
Even in her final days,

07:29.530 --> 07:30.970
he barely showed up.

07:39.560 --> 07:41.510
They were college classmates.

07:43.830 --> 07:47.070
My mom was well protected by my grandpa since childhood.

07:47.870 --> 07:48.950
She was naive and innocent.

07:51.159 --> 07:52.560
After he won my mom over,

07:52.860 --> 07:54.060
they got married

07:54.720 --> 07:56.040
and had me.

07:57.960 --> 08:00.310
But he was never ready to take responsibility.

08:02.810 --> 08:04.690
After getting accepted into a master's program in Bei City,

08:05.510 --> 08:07.680
he made my mom leave Hang City to be with him.

08:08.870 --> 08:10.160
But once they got there,

08:11.240 --> 08:13.720
he threw himself into his studies and research,

08:14.270 --> 08:16.000
leaving my mom to fend for herself.

08:18.980 --> 08:20.780
Not only did she have to finish her own studies,

08:20.800 --> 08:21.880
but she also had to take care of me.

08:24.160 --> 08:26.510
Day after day, the exhaustion and stress piled up,

08:27.220 --> 08:28.430
and she developed breast cancer.

08:30.430 --> 08:32.120
She passed away before she even turned 40.

08:48.930 --> 08:50.250
It's been so many years.

08:50.960 --> 08:53.200
I've gotten used to this kind of relationship with him.

08:54.870 --> 08:55.720
That's it.

09:08.390 --> 09:09.390
He Suye,

09:09.890 --> 09:11.490
actually, there's another reason

09:11.520 --> 09:12.880
I came today.

09:13.630 --> 09:15.250
You're giving a presentation tomorrow,

09:15.350 --> 09:16.710
so make sure to dress nicely.

09:16.960 --> 09:18.030
People will be taking pictures.

09:19.320 --> 09:21.240
There's no need to be dressy.

09:21.240 --> 09:22.630
I'll just throw on something casual.

09:22.660 --> 09:24.280
No way! You have to look sharp.

09:24.650 --> 09:26.010
Hurry up and finish this.

09:26.040 --> 09:27.110
Then I'll help you pick an outfit.

09:28.050 --> 09:28.640
Come on.

09:29.590 --> 09:30.160
Alright.

09:37.510 --> 09:38.030
You eat too.

11:07.120 --> 11:09.050
[Chinese Medical Association]
[The 8th Summer Summit]

12:09.980 --> 12:15.040
[Research on Improving the Quality of Life of Late-Stage Breast Cancer Patients through TCM]

12:11.030 --> 12:13.440
Distinguished leaders, experts, and guests,

12:13.440 --> 12:15.480
welcome to

12:15.480 --> 12:16.390
the TCM session of this summit.

12:16.870 --> 12:18.580
The first topic in this session

12:18.600 --> 12:21.650
is a research project on TCM treatments

12:21.680 --> 12:22.870
for breast cancer,

12:22.890 --> 12:25.010
led by the young physician He Suye.

12:25.270 --> 12:27.120
Now, let's welcome Dr. He Suye

12:27.320 --> 12:28.510
with a round of applause.

12:42.600 --> 12:43.550
Good morning,

12:43.550 --> 12:44.840
esteemed experts.

12:45.120 --> 12:48.000
I'm He Suye from the Oncology Department

12:48.020 --> 12:49.210
of Jiangzhou TCM University Hospital.

12:50.120 --> 12:51.790
I'm honored to have this opportunity today

12:51.790 --> 12:53.630
to share my insights with all of you.

12:53.630 --> 12:55.080
I look forward to

12:55.080 --> 12:57.240
your critiques and guidance.

12:57.630 --> 12:59.270
My research

12:59.270 --> 13:02.120
focuses on improving the quality of life

13:02.120 --> 13:03.440
of late-stage breast cancer patients

13:03.440 --> 13:05.270
through specialized TCM therapies.

13:06.320 --> 13:07.870
Nowadays, for most

13:07.870 --> 13:09.360
breast cancer patients,

13:09.630 --> 13:11.320
various clinical symptoms

13:11.320 --> 13:13.600
significantly impact their quality of life.

13:14.000 --> 13:14.840
However,

13:14.840 --> 13:17.480
current medical efforts tend to

13:17.480 --> 13:18.630
prioritize tumor control

13:18.630 --> 13:19.840
and extending lifespan,

13:20.080 --> 13:20.750
while the improvement of patients' overall well-being…

13:20.750 --> 13:21.790
You startled me.

13:22.150 --> 13:24.480
You came just in time. It just began.

13:25.240 --> 13:27.000
From this chart, we can see that

13:27.000 --> 13:29.000
TCM has distinct advantages

13:29.240 --> 13:31.150
in symptom management.

13:31.510 --> 13:32.840
Therefore, this time,

13:32.840 --> 13:34.120
my team and I

13:34.120 --> 13:36.910
chose to explore the use of TCM therapies

13:36.910 --> 13:39.440
for late-stage breast cancer patients

13:39.440 --> 13:41.750
to improve their quality of life.

13:41.750 --> 13:42.670
As shown

13:42.670 --> 13:44.270
in the table,

13:44.790 --> 13:46.790
there is a significant improvement

13:46.790 --> 13:50.630
in symptom scores for TCM treatments

13:50.630 --> 13:52.910
and in alleviating cancer-related fatigue.

14:53.700 --> 14:55.820
Therefore, our study concludes that

14:56.320 --> 14:57.720
combining modern medicine

14:57.720 --> 14:59.120
with specialized TCM therapies

14:59.120 --> 15:01.550
not only extends the lifespan

15:01.550 --> 15:03.080
of late-stage breast cancer patients

15:03.080 --> 15:04.670
and helps control

15:04.670 --> 15:05.840
tumor progression

15:05.990 --> 15:08.130
-but also enhances their quality of life.
-I gotta go.

15:08.300 --> 15:09.940
It effectively alleviates clinical symptoms

15:10.390 --> 15:12.030
and mitigates treatment-related

15:12.030 --> 15:13.480
adverse effects.

15:14.070 --> 15:15.790
At last, I sincerely thank

15:15.790 --> 15:17.630
all my colleagues and patients who participated in this study.

15:17.840 --> 15:19.360
That concludes my presentation.

15:19.720 --> 15:20.630
I look forward to

15:20.630 --> 15:22.120
your critiques and guidance.

15:36.200 --> 15:36.830
Thank you.

15:36.970 --> 15:38.050
Thank you, Dr. He Suye,

15:38.080 --> 15:39.240
for this insightful

15:39.240 --> 15:40.550
presentation.

15:41.040 --> 15:41.720
I'm sure

15:41.720 --> 15:42.840
everyone has noticed

15:42.840 --> 15:45.270
how outstanding Dr. He Suye is.

15:45.270 --> 15:47.030
He's a true role model for young doctors.

15:47.030 --> 15:48.720
We should all learn from him.

15:50.750 --> 15:52.030
It's from a fan of yours.

16:00.150 --> 16:01.600
Alright. Next,

16:01.600 --> 16:02.390
let's move on

16:02.390 --> 16:04.210
to the next physician

16:04.230 --> 16:05.910
in the TCM session

16:05.940 --> 16:07.210
who will share his insights with us.

16:07.520 --> 16:10.400
I bet you've all heard about him.

16:10.420 --> 16:12.180
With a strong foundation in clinical practice…

16:12.210 --> 16:14.170
Grandpa, I have to go out for a moment.

16:14.510 --> 16:16.320
He's also the youngest doctoral advisor

16:16.320 --> 16:19.120
in cardiology in the country.

16:19.150 --> 16:20.630
Let's welcome him with applause.

16:28.240 --> 16:29.200
The conference is almost over.

16:29.200 --> 16:30.200
Have Food & Beverage come over

16:30.200 --> 16:31.870
to deal with the leftover food.

16:32.100 --> 16:34.220
And once the event ends tonight, clear out the venue.

16:34.250 --> 16:35.250
Don't leave anything behind.

16:36.240 --> 16:37.240
I'll get back to work.

16:37.510 --> 16:38.200
Bye-bye.

16:40.960 --> 16:41.720
Xifan.

16:58.550 --> 16:59.480
You're already here.

16:59.780 --> 17:01.060
Why are you leaving without telling me?

17:03.760 --> 17:04.710
He Suye.

17:04.960 --> 17:05.930
He Suye.

17:06.490 --> 17:07.530
There are too many people here.

17:12.119 --> 17:14.230
I just wanted to see your presentation.

17:14.260 --> 17:15.000
If I had stayed,

17:15.000 --> 17:16.640
I might have gotten in the way of your work.

17:17.710 --> 17:19.119
So, how do you think I did?

17:21.650 --> 17:22.730
I think

17:23.069 --> 17:25.510
you totally did justice to the outfit I picked for you.

17:26.020 --> 17:28.390
My boyfriend looks super handsome today.

17:29.270 --> 17:31.320
Of course. Who do you think picked this outfit for me?

17:35.830 --> 17:36.510
By the way,

17:37.140 --> 17:38.320
did you see

17:38.460 --> 17:39.590
Mr. Shen in there?

17:44.920 --> 17:46.030
You invited him?

17:50.560 --> 17:52.670
I ran into him last night.

17:52.960 --> 17:54.200
We talked for a bit.

17:54.480 --> 17:57.170
He's really concerned about your work and your life.

17:58.880 --> 17:59.840
How about this?

17:59.870 --> 18:00.800
Tonight,

18:01.230 --> 18:02.430
let's have dinner together.

18:03.030 --> 18:04.800
I'd love to get to know Mr. Shen.

18:05.170 --> 18:05.730
What do you say?

18:07.050 --> 18:07.920
What do you say?

18:08.070 --> 18:08.880
Dinner?

18:09.110 --> 18:10.110
Maybe next time.

18:17.750 --> 18:18.550
Mr. He.

18:29.440 --> 18:30.590
Your research topic is great.

18:31.120 --> 18:32.320
It has great academic value.

18:34.360 --> 18:35.080
Thank you.

18:39.750 --> 18:41.480
Actually, in the future,

18:41.480 --> 18:44.330
combining cardiac surgery with TCM

18:45.010 --> 18:47.140
could also be a promising direction.

18:55.740 --> 18:57.260
Alright, you two chat.

18:57.280 --> 18:58.170
I won't disturb you anymore.

19:02.990 --> 19:03.840
He Suye.

19:09.000 --> 19:09.650
Dad.

19:21.790 --> 19:23.600
Are you free tonight?

19:28.510 --> 19:29.400
How about

19:29.770 --> 19:31.010
we have dinner together?

19:33.640 --> 19:34.350
Sure.

19:34.840 --> 19:36.360
I happen to be free tonight.

19:37.530 --> 19:38.450
I'll make the arrangements.

19:41.850 --> 19:42.570
Okay.

20:11.110 --> 20:12.030
Come on.

20:13.140 --> 20:13.860
Thank you.

20:18.850 --> 20:20.680
This restaurant has been around for a long time.

20:20.710 --> 20:22.080
The flavors are on the lighter side.

20:22.100 --> 20:24.010
I'm not sure if you all will like it.

20:24.260 --> 20:25.350
These dishes are good.

20:26.870 --> 20:29.550
They adjust their menu according to the seasons,

20:29.570 --> 20:31.440
offering medicinal dishes that clear heat and eliminate dampness.

20:32.720 --> 20:33.750
Given what you said,

20:33.750 --> 20:35.270
Shen,

20:35.270 --> 20:37.480
you seem to know quite a bit about TCM.

20:37.480 --> 20:39.480
Not really, just the basics.

20:39.840 --> 20:41.920
I took Chinese medicine for a while before,

20:41.940 --> 20:43.490
and I also worked on

20:43.520 --> 20:45.210
a medicated diet project with He Suye.

20:46.020 --> 20:47.150
You took Chinese medicine?

20:47.240 --> 20:49.480
You were dealing with some health issues?

20:50.130 --> 20:51.240
I had insomnia at the time.

20:52.350 --> 20:54.280
She had trouble sleeping for over half a year.

20:54.300 --> 20:55.680
I helped her with it,

20:55.810 --> 20:56.850
and she's much better now.

20:59.110 --> 21:00.000
The two of them

21:00.000 --> 21:02.150
met when she was seeking treatment.

21:02.170 --> 21:02.810
Really?

21:02.840 --> 21:04.270
It must be fate.

21:05.270 --> 21:06.350
One day,

21:06.350 --> 21:08.400
Suye came back all excited,

21:08.850 --> 21:10.850
telling me about a strange patient he met.

21:11.670 --> 21:12.740
This patient

21:12.990 --> 21:16.320
knew a lot about medicinal herbs

21:16.610 --> 21:18.410
and even bargained with Suye,

21:18.440 --> 21:21.200
insisting on writing her own prescription.

21:21.950 --> 21:23.430
What kind of patient was that?

21:23.690 --> 21:24.900
So I told him, "Don't treat her.

21:24.930 --> 21:27.170
Let her find another doctor."

21:27.560 --> 21:29.120
But Suye wouldn't listen.

21:29.180 --> 21:32.000
Instead, he told me it was a young lady

21:32.530 --> 21:34.240
and went on and on about

21:34.350 --> 21:36.400
how beautiful and elegant she was.

21:36.430 --> 21:37.700
Then I realized—

21:37.720 --> 21:40.130
this wasn't about treating a patient.

21:40.150 --> 21:41.460
He had other intentions.

21:41.490 --> 21:43.420
He was interested in the girl.

21:44.000 --> 21:44.810
Enough, Grandpa.

21:45.440 --> 21:46.240
Here. Let's not talk about that.

21:46.240 --> 21:46.700
Here.

21:48.320 --> 21:49.080
Interesting.

21:51.070 --> 21:52.160
Your desserts are here.

21:52.440 --> 21:53.370
Here come the desserts.

21:57.990 --> 21:58.840
Thank you.

22:00.350 --> 22:01.200
Alright.

22:01.200 --> 22:02.110
Please enjoy.

22:05.160 --> 22:06.200
What kind of soup is this?

22:07.410 --> 22:09.650
It's a soup made with lily bulbs, lotus seeds, and fox nuts.

22:09.680 --> 22:11.370
He Suye specifically ordered it.

22:19.040 --> 22:20.170
Fox nut soup?

22:25.030 --> 22:25.550
Yes.

22:26.230 --> 22:28.600
I had this soup a lot as a kid.

22:30.920 --> 22:32.270
Your mom loved

22:32.270 --> 22:34.240
making this for us.

22:35.020 --> 22:37.480
Back when we first moved to Bei City,

22:37.640 --> 22:40.200
she really loved fox nuts,

22:40.230 --> 22:42.440
but it was hard to find fresh ones at the market.

22:42.970 --> 22:46.050
So she bought dried fox nuts to make soup for us instead.

22:59.210 --> 23:00.140
This is authentic.

23:00.610 --> 23:01.330
Try it.

23:01.800 --> 23:03.150
Does it taste like it did when you were young?

23:13.030 --> 23:13.790
Delicious?

23:14.400 --> 23:16.270
Shen, how old are you?

23:16.720 --> 23:18.070
I'm 28.

23:18.240 --> 23:19.680
You're not very young.

23:21.350 --> 23:22.660
I want to ask—

23:22.900 --> 23:25.060
do you two plan to get married?

23:31.270 --> 23:32.640
There's no rush.

23:33.370 --> 23:35.900
Xifan is going to study abroad in October.

23:36.110 --> 23:38.180
We'll think about marriage after she comes back.

23:45.120 --> 23:46.440
Every generation

23:46.440 --> 23:48.610
has its own way of life.

23:49.070 --> 23:51.550
For young people these days,

23:52.150 --> 23:55.060
falling in love is simply about following their hearts.

23:55.720 --> 23:57.280
As for marriage,

23:57.660 --> 24:00.980
it's more of a contractual agreement between two people.

24:01.600 --> 24:03.270
It's an important life decision.

24:04.850 --> 24:06.240
At my age…

24:06.270 --> 24:06.960
Well…

24:07.000 --> 24:07.440
I…

24:07.440 --> 24:08.310
Have some soup.

24:08.550 --> 24:09.350
Okay, okay.

24:09.350 --> 24:10.000
While it's hot.

24:11.820 --> 24:12.770
So sweet.

24:13.900 --> 24:14.920
No hard feelings.

24:14.920 --> 24:16.230
I was just asking.

24:17.070 --> 24:17.640
It's fine.

24:21.850 --> 24:22.850
I'll be back soon.

24:22.880 --> 24:23.640
Okay.

24:36.020 --> 24:36.500
Dad.

24:37.450 --> 24:38.450
You came at the right time.

24:40.850 --> 24:43.000
This is my first time having dinner with her.

24:43.020 --> 24:45.220
I shouldn't have pushed you for marriage.

24:45.250 --> 24:46.250
Can you explain it to her for me?

24:46.270 --> 24:47.850
It's okay. She's very understanding.

24:47.870 --> 24:48.590
She won't mind.

24:48.940 --> 24:49.790
That's good.

24:52.670 --> 24:54.390
I really think she's a great girl.

24:54.670 --> 24:55.670
Don't let her slip away.

24:56.270 --> 24:56.940
I know.

24:58.200 --> 24:59.770
How are things between you two?

25:00.390 --> 25:01.230
Pretty good.

25:01.650 --> 25:02.410
Well,

25:02.440 --> 25:04.130
we haven't been together for very long,

25:04.150 --> 25:05.740
so we still need more time

25:05.770 --> 25:07.180
to get to know each other better.

25:07.590 --> 25:08.900
I don't want her to

25:08.930 --> 25:10.380
regret being with me.

25:12.310 --> 25:13.110
That's right.

25:13.810 --> 25:15.490
It's a big life decision, after all.

25:15.840 --> 25:17.120
You have to think it through

25:17.950 --> 25:20.120
and consider every aspect.

25:21.700 --> 25:24.420
It's being responsible to yourself and to her.

25:28.810 --> 25:30.160
Don't end up like your mom and me.

25:30.160 --> 25:30.590
Dad.

25:33.540 --> 25:34.580
Let's not

25:34.610 --> 25:35.570
bring up the past.

25:42.510 --> 25:43.440
Well,

25:44.020 --> 25:45.020
let's stay in touch.

25:45.400 --> 25:47.510
I'll keep you updated if anything comes up.

25:49.730 --> 25:50.350
Thank you.

25:57.510 --> 25:58.950
When's your flight tomorrow?

26:01.000 --> 26:02.170
Do you want to

26:02.640 --> 26:03.710
visit Mom with me?

26:04.810 --> 26:06.000
I'm leaving in the afternoon.

26:06.030 --> 26:06.880
Don't worry about it.

26:06.900 --> 26:08.450
I'll go see her by myself in the morning.

26:09.920 --> 26:10.350
Alright.

26:11.000 --> 26:13.310
Also, I found some papers

26:13.310 --> 26:16.070
on combining cardiac surgery with TCM.

26:16.110 --> 26:17.280
I'll send them to you later.

26:17.630 --> 26:18.440
If you have time,

26:18.440 --> 26:19.240
take a look.

26:19.550 --> 26:20.300
If you're interested,

26:20.740 --> 26:21.830
maybe we can study

26:22.050 --> 26:23.770
and discuss it together

26:23.790 --> 26:24.900
in the future.

26:34.290 --> 26:35.000
Thank you.

27:04.200 --> 27:05.170
He Suye.

27:06.090 --> 27:08.610
When Mr. Shen was drinking the fox nut soup,

27:08.830 --> 27:10.700
it seemed like you wanted to say something.

27:13.490 --> 27:15.060
I just thought of my mom.

27:16.030 --> 27:18.590
When she made this soup,

27:18.950 --> 27:20.640
she always set aside a bowl of it for my dad,

27:21.480 --> 27:23.310
saying he loved it very much.

27:24.750 --> 27:25.960
Turns out,

27:25.960 --> 27:27.960
they always cared for each other.

27:45.160 --> 27:46.000
Xifan.

27:49.400 --> 27:50.480
I have something for you.

28:10.270 --> 28:11.310
This bracelet

28:14.240 --> 28:15.750
was left to me by my mom.

28:21.010 --> 28:22.100
Let me put it on you.

28:55.010 --> 28:56.960
Why are you suddenly giving this to me?

29:03.950 --> 29:05.320
I just suddenly feel…

29:11.310 --> 29:12.440
that I love you so much.

29:13.050 --> 29:16.510
♫Watching the snow fall, flake by flake♫

29:16.540 --> 29:20.020
♫Slowly melting away my thoughts♫

29:20.000 --> 29:21.200
I love you too.

29:20.050 --> 29:23.500
♫Smiling, I wave goodbye as you head home♫

29:23.680 --> 29:27.260
♫But I never said those words♫

29:27.290 --> 29:30.810
♫Watching the snow fall, flake by flake♫

29:30.910 --> 29:34.730
♫When will love bloom into a flower?♫

29:34.750 --> 29:40.440
♫You wander the world, forgetting to reply♫

29:40.630 --> 29:44.220
♫When you turn around, I'll be right there♫

29:54.930 --> 29:55.820
Thank you.

30:14.790 --> 30:16.680
Give me more of those little rice balls.

30:16.680 --> 30:17.200
Okay.

30:17.200 --> 30:18.350
As you wish.

30:18.350 --> 30:19.310
That's delicious.

30:21.700 --> 30:22.500
Try it.

30:23.350 --> 30:24.150
Did you add sugar?

30:24.150 --> 30:24.740
Yeah.

30:24.740 --> 30:25.150
It's hot.

30:25.150 --> 30:25.980
What are you doing?

30:25.980 --> 30:26.500
It's hot.

30:26.500 --> 30:27.060
Give it to me.

30:27.060 --> 30:27.590
It's hot.

30:30.700 --> 30:31.460
It's not sweet enough.

30:32.220 --> 30:32.950
It's really not sweet enough.

30:32.950 --> 30:33.630
Add more sugar.

30:33.630 --> 30:34.060
It's…

30:34.060 --> 30:34.500
It's too sweet!

30:34.500 --> 30:35.220
It doesn't taste good.

30:35.220 --> 30:36.020
Stop. No more sugar.

30:36.020 --> 30:36.590
I mean it.

30:36.590 --> 30:37.430
Enough, enough.

30:38.080 --> 30:38.920
Add more sugar.

30:38.950 --> 30:39.780
Come on.

30:39.970 --> 30:41.150
Enough, enough.

30:42.570 --> 30:43.480
You're back.

30:43.510 --> 30:44.620
I didn't hear you come in.

30:47.870 --> 30:48.870
Oh my goodness.

30:49.700 --> 30:51.220
It's from Dr. He?

30:53.390 --> 30:54.740
He's so sweet.

30:55.070 --> 30:56.700
He really knows how to pick gifts.

30:56.730 --> 30:59.190
Look how perfectly this bracelet suits

30:59.190 --> 31:00.520
our daughter's temperament.

31:01.150 --> 31:03.670
Ms. Shen, your mom thinks it's not sweet enough.

31:03.950 --> 31:05.260
Try a sip.

31:06.020 --> 31:06.670
Is it good?

31:06.670 --> 31:07.430
It's just right.

31:08.110 --> 31:09.780
Because I added sugar just now.

31:09.780 --> 31:10.830
She agrees with me.

31:10.830 --> 31:12.670
I've already added a spoonful of sugar.

31:12.670 --> 31:13.740
Try it again.

31:13.740 --> 31:14.430
It has more sugar now.

31:15.220 --> 31:16.630
I want a little rice ball.

31:16.890 --> 31:17.890
Okay.

31:20.830 --> 31:21.630
Good?

31:21.630 --> 31:21.980
Here.

31:22.380 --> 31:23.140
This bowl

31:23.630 --> 31:24.430
is for your mom.

31:24.870 --> 31:25.910
Let me get a bowl of it for you.

31:45.430 --> 31:46.980
Alright. Just leave me here.

31:46.980 --> 31:47.870
Give it to me.

31:48.600 --> 31:50.300
You've taken such good care of me.

31:50.300 --> 31:50.830
Thank you.

31:51.300 --> 31:53.060
Not at all. It's my job.

31:55.720 --> 31:58.290
Please, look out for Suye.

31:59.300 --> 32:00.430
Don't worry.

32:00.890 --> 32:03.450
If you have time, you should visit more often.

32:04.090 --> 32:07.090
He Suye really cares about you.

32:11.220 --> 32:13.900
Anyway, I'm really glad

32:13.920 --> 32:15.010
to see you two together.

32:16.410 --> 32:16.930
Oh, right,

32:17.300 --> 32:19.150
I suddenly brought up marriage yesterday.

32:19.150 --> 32:20.190
I didn't scare you, did I?

32:21.870 --> 32:22.750
It's alright.

32:23.280 --> 32:25.130
Good. I'll be going now.

32:26.350 --> 32:26.940
Goodbye.

33:38.130 --> 33:38.930
Alright.

33:46.310 --> 33:48.100
Mr. He has checked out and left for the airport.

33:53.980 --> 33:54.950
I want to see you.

34:14.199 --> 34:15.070
Where's the bracelet?

34:16.659 --> 34:18.230
The hotel has a dress code—

34:18.230 --> 34:20.270
no jewelry during work hours.

34:22.179 --> 34:22.980
Okay.

34:24.610 --> 34:25.429
Dr. He,

34:25.980 --> 34:27.060
you're smiling.

34:27.060 --> 34:28.659
Are you texting your girlfriend?

34:29.639 --> 34:30.909
You look so happy.

34:49.460 --> 34:50.460
He, He.

34:50.460 --> 34:51.179
Look.

34:51.710 --> 34:53.620
Your photo from yesterday's presentation

34:53.620 --> 34:54.980
was posted on the hospital's official account.

34:55.710 --> 34:57.540
Not bad. You look pretty sharp.

34:59.140 --> 35:01.350
My girlfriend picked that outfit for me.

35:04.920 --> 35:07.040
Dr. He, that's too much.

35:07.530 --> 35:09.090
I talked to you about work,

35:09.180 --> 35:10.810
and you answered something about your outfit.

35:11.180 --> 35:12.340
Did I ask about your outfit?

35:12.370 --> 35:13.810
Did I?

35:14.620 --> 35:15.660
Dr. Song,

35:16.140 --> 35:18.500
what's bothering you isn't his outfit

35:18.900 --> 35:20.380
but the fact that he has a girlfriend.

35:21.360 --> 35:23.880
Head Nurse, it's a bit rude of you to say that.

35:23.900 --> 35:26.060
I used to worry about his love life.

35:26.090 --> 35:27.130
Now it's your turn.

35:27.500 --> 35:29.230
Look how happy he is now,

35:29.230 --> 35:30.840
and look at you.

35:31.050 --> 35:32.860
You really need to step it up.

35:33.040 --> 35:34.480
What more can I do to step it up?

35:34.500 --> 35:37.540
I've done everything I could.

35:38.020 --> 35:38.880
You know what?

35:39.080 --> 35:41.170
I dream about getting into a relationship.

35:41.190 --> 35:42.270
I can't even imagine

35:42.310 --> 35:43.350
how well I'd treat my girlfriend

35:43.350 --> 35:44.660
if I ever got one.

35:44.660 --> 35:46.350
Why is it that someone as outstanding as me

35:46.350 --> 35:47.980
doesn't have a girlfriend?

35:47.980 --> 35:48.830
Here. It's done.

35:49.790 --> 35:50.670
I'm off duty.

35:51.020 --> 35:53.230
You stay here and reflect on that.

35:54.090 --> 35:55.090
Keep me company for a bit.

35:56.660 --> 35:58.430
Remember the girl I introduced you to last time?

35:58.430 --> 35:59.140
How do you like her?

35:59.580 --> 36:00.660
Don't you start.

36:01.140 --> 36:02.390
She blocked me.

36:02.390 --> 36:03.020
See for yourself.

36:03.020 --> 36:04.350
I have no idea why.

36:04.480 --> 36:05.520
No way!

36:05.540 --> 36:06.890
She really blocked me.

36:06.920 --> 36:07.810
Look.

36:08.610 --> 36:09.880
You're just unreliable.

36:09.980 --> 36:10.980
What did you say to her?

36:10.980 --> 36:12.660
It's your fault. This is on you.

36:12.660 --> 36:13.950
You owe me a meal.

36:24.540 --> 36:26.060
Come on. Stop wasting time.

36:26.060 --> 36:27.100
Let's go, let's go.

36:27.100 --> 36:27.910
We're heading out!

36:27.910 --> 36:29.020
Where are you going?

36:30.060 --> 36:30.950
Didn't you tell her?

36:31.140 --> 36:32.140
Weren't you supposed to tell her?

36:32.310 --> 36:33.350
I forgot.

36:34.500 --> 36:37.580
We're going to a farm stay with my colleagues.

36:37.580 --> 36:38.750
We'll be back tomorrow evening.

36:40.180 --> 36:40.620
Okay.

36:41.180 --> 36:42.140
What are you doing?

36:42.290 --> 36:43.360
Just crunching some numbers.

36:43.620 --> 36:44.550
I did the math.

36:44.750 --> 36:46.230
If I work for two more months,

36:46.230 --> 36:47.800
I'll have enough for my living expenses.

36:47.980 --> 36:49.310
And with some commission,

36:49.310 --> 36:51.100
I can quit my job next month.

36:51.100 --> 36:52.180
No need to calculate.

36:52.300 --> 36:53.140
If you're short on money,

36:53.140 --> 36:55.660
your dad has a secret stash. Ask him for help.

36:57.230 --> 36:58.060
No secret stash.

36:58.060 --> 36:59.180
He'd be more than happy to help.

36:59.180 --> 36:59.980
He said it himself.

36:59.980 --> 37:01.350
No secret stash.

37:01.500 --> 37:02.140
While we're not at home,

37:02.140 --> 37:03.430
what do you plan to do?

37:04.100 --> 37:06.480
I'm gonna go out to eat something nice

37:06.580 --> 37:09.130
and then ask He Suye out for a date.

37:10.950 --> 37:12.270
A date is fine,

37:12.580 --> 37:13.620
but come home early

37:14.060 --> 37:14.950
and get enough rest.

37:14.950 --> 37:15.750
Got it, got it.

37:15.750 --> 37:16.540
Don't worry.

37:17.660 --> 37:18.910
You two have fun.

37:18.980 --> 37:19.750
Alright!

37:19.870 --> 37:20.910
Bye-bye.

37:20.910 --> 37:21.290
Let's go.

37:21.350 --> 37:22.500
Bring a gift back for me.

37:22.500 --> 37:23.270
Sure!

37:23.270 --> 37:25.320
What gift? What's there to buy at a farm stay?

37:25.350 --> 37:26.150
Cornbread, maybe.

37:35.830 --> 37:36.310
This place

37:36.310 --> 37:37.390
was recommended by Xifan.

37:37.390 --> 37:38.270
Try the food.

37:39.070 --> 37:39.950
It's not bad, right?

37:40.430 --> 37:41.060
How is it?

37:41.460 --> 37:42.020
Delicious.

37:42.020 --> 37:42.830
Let's have a toast.

37:43.930 --> 37:47.220
Here is to another successfully completed major event!

37:47.240 --> 37:48.200
Congratulations!

37:50.130 --> 37:52.180
Are you sure there are no more big events coming up?

37:52.210 --> 37:53.000
Absolutely sure.

37:55.240 --> 37:57.280
Then I can finally relax and wait to resign.

37:58.020 --> 37:58.830
Xifan,

37:59.100 --> 38:00.310
when are you resigning?

38:00.310 --> 38:01.540
I can't wait.

38:01.950 --> 38:03.660
I'm planning to resign next month.

38:03.660 --> 38:05.020
After I wrap up the OA system and the handover,

38:05.020 --> 38:06.230
it'll be around August.

38:06.230 --> 38:07.820
Then I can properly prepare for studying abroad.

38:08.750 --> 38:09.950
Sounds like a solid plan.

38:14.180 --> 38:14.500
Well,

38:14.500 --> 38:16.870
Dr. He, I want to ask you something.

38:17.140 --> 38:17.710
If…

38:18.350 --> 38:19.100
If I were to open

38:19.100 --> 38:21.750
a medicinal cuisine restaurant,

38:21.930 --> 38:24.090
would you be willing to be my consultant?

38:24.980 --> 38:26.390
And about the ingredient supply.

38:26.390 --> 38:28.790
That herbal farm we visited last time,

38:28.790 --> 38:30.310
do you think they could be my supplier?

38:30.710 --> 38:31.980
Of course, no problem at all.

38:32.770 --> 38:35.270
But what made you suddenly want to do that?

38:35.420 --> 38:37.580
She just wants to take on a challenging business.

38:40.780 --> 38:42.270
Well, a client of mine

38:42.270 --> 38:43.140
owns a restaurant,

38:43.140 --> 38:44.460
but it isn't doing well.

38:44.460 --> 38:46.870
So he wants me to take over as the general manager,

38:47.060 --> 38:47.980
basically meaning

38:48.390 --> 38:49.980
I'll run the restaurant for him.

38:49.980 --> 38:52.310
That way, I don't have to worry about rent,

38:52.310 --> 38:53.980
and I get a lot of decision-making power.

38:53.980 --> 38:54.780
Isn't that great?

38:56.310 --> 38:58.240
I've already secured a professional consultant.

38:58.750 --> 38:59.910
Aren't I super reliable?

39:00.270 --> 39:01.270
Yeah, absolutely.

39:01.270 --> 39:02.100
Super reliable.

39:02.430 --> 39:02.930
Come on.

39:03.370 --> 39:05.300
Let's raise a toast to our handsome Dr. He.

39:05.620 --> 39:06.500
What for?

39:06.660 --> 39:08.350
About the consulting fee

39:08.350 --> 39:09.660
and the prices of medicinal ingredients,

39:09.660 --> 39:10.310
can you maybe…

39:11.140 --> 39:12.060
give her a little discount?

39:12.090 --> 39:14.410
Of course. It's my family's business.

39:14.460 --> 39:16.500
I should be thanking you instead.

39:18.640 --> 39:19.910
Your family's business?

39:20.580 --> 39:21.020
Yep.

39:21.280 --> 39:22.420
It's his family's business.

39:22.750 --> 39:24.870
When he invited us to that herbal farm,

39:24.870 --> 39:26.790
he actually meant to show off.

39:26.790 --> 39:27.910
I just didn't catch on.

39:27.910 --> 39:29.350
No. My grandpa wanted to show off.

39:29.350 --> 39:29.910
Fine, fine,

39:29.910 --> 39:30.750
it was your grandpa's idea.

39:30.750 --> 39:31.710
Alright.

39:31.710 --> 39:32.310
A toast to you all!

39:32.310 --> 39:32.950
Cheers!

39:32.950 --> 39:34.750
So the herbal farm belongs to you.

39:34.750 --> 39:36.100
To my grandpa.

39:37.060 --> 39:38.310
Why not get married on the mountain?

39:38.310 --> 39:39.750
Your family owns three mountains.

39:42.580 --> 39:44.310
Thank you for using WeChat Pay.

39:44.710 --> 39:45.950
That's done. I'll get you the receipt in a moment.

39:45.950 --> 39:46.660
Thank you very much.

39:46.660 --> 39:47.430
Let me pay. Let me pay.

39:47.430 --> 39:48.450
I already paid.

39:48.470 --> 39:50.020
You should've let me pay.

39:50.690 --> 39:52.440
I didn't make it last time you went drinking,

39:52.460 --> 39:53.620
so I should pay for it this time.

39:54.470 --> 39:55.630
Next time it's on me.

39:55.650 --> 39:56.170
Okay.

40:05.180 --> 40:07.850
Are you worrying about Xiangya's business?

40:09.770 --> 40:10.770
Yeah, a little.

40:13.710 --> 40:15.020
You know how she is—

40:15.500 --> 40:16.390
impulsive,

40:17.220 --> 40:18.140
and…

40:20.310 --> 40:21.980
she doesn't always think things through.

40:22.740 --> 40:24.660
I'm just worried that if she runs into problems,

40:24.790 --> 40:25.710
she'll be stressed out.

40:26.870 --> 40:27.880
Isn't that exactly

40:28.060 --> 40:30.430
where you come in?

40:32.020 --> 40:32.830
That's true.

40:35.000 --> 40:36.690
What do you think about Xifan studying abroad?

40:40.500 --> 40:41.870
I'm not too worried.

40:42.710 --> 40:44.180
I don't want her to have regrets.

40:44.890 --> 40:47.000
So whatever she wants to do,

40:47.030 --> 40:49.470
whether it's studying abroad or anything else, I'll fully support her.

40:54.620 --> 40:55.820
Alright, don't overthink it.

40:55.850 --> 40:56.650
They're waiting for us.

40:57.090 --> 40:57.760
Let's go.

41:07.310 --> 41:08.140
What are you thinking about?

41:09.620 --> 41:11.490
Even though I've planned for a while

41:11.520 --> 41:14.650
that Xiangya and I would resign after the medical summit,

41:15.140 --> 41:16.950
today is the first time it feels real.

41:17.520 --> 41:19.050
We're really going to part ways.

41:20.230 --> 41:21.770
After graduating from university,

41:21.900 --> 41:23.790
we started working at the hotel together.

41:24.310 --> 41:26.980
And now, maybe as Senior Lin said,

41:26.980 --> 41:30.460
he's going to work all alone at Gunan Huating.

41:32.980 --> 41:34.610
Sticking to the same job

41:34.700 --> 41:37.140
for seven years

41:37.450 --> 41:38.780
right out of college—

41:39.470 --> 41:40.640
that's not easy.

41:41.870 --> 41:42.730
And through all these years,

41:44.540 --> 41:46.500
you've looked after each other

41:46.830 --> 41:47.710
and accompanied each other.

41:48.620 --> 41:50.950
These years are indeed memorable.

41:52.950 --> 41:56.100
Seven years, a full seven years.

41:56.830 --> 41:59.460
I guess I can say my career at Gunan Huating

41:59.460 --> 42:01.870
has come to a perfect close.

42:03.460 --> 42:04.390
What do you mean?

42:05.260 --> 42:08.700
Think about it. I achieved my career goals.

42:09.270 --> 42:12.340
I got to see you give a presentation

42:12.540 --> 42:14.820
at a major event.

42:15.500 --> 42:17.710
And I even witnessed you making peace with Mr. He.

42:18.010 --> 42:20.450
I genuinely feel happy

42:20.910 --> 42:21.950
and content.

42:27.580 --> 42:28.390
Yeah.

42:29.260 --> 42:30.450
I genuinely…

42:32.650 --> 42:33.770
feel content too.
